te><p>and who could possibly forget</p><blockquote><p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.hotchicksdigsmartmen.com/2010/10/donors-choose-science-rules.html\">Janiece at Hot Chicks Dig Smart Men</a>.</p></blockquote><p>Thanks! Every little push helps.</p><p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/XV1KtGQivU0tAz2JS2zvvG8NX-U/0/da\"><img src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/XV1KtGQivU0tAz2JS2zvvG8NX-U/0/di\" border=\"0\" ismap></a><br/><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/XV1KtGQivU0tAz2JS2zvvG8NX-U/1/da\"><img src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/XV1KtGQivU0tAz2JS2zvvG8NX-U/1/di\" border=\"0\" ismap></a></p><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/CosmicVarianceBlog/~4/rt9KfavAnyk\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\"/></a><div class=\"feedflare\"><a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DiscoverMag?a=R126BExi4EI:oLGw6E7EG1s:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DiscoverMag?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\"></img></a><a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DiscoverMag?a=R126BExi4EI:oLGw6E7EG1s:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DiscoverMag?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" border=\"0\"></img></a><a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DiscoverMag?a=R126BExi4EI:oLGw6E7EG1s:F7zBnMyn0Lo\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DiscoverMag?i=R126BExi4EI:oLGw6E7EG1s:F7zBnMyn0Lo\" border=\"0\"></img></a><a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DiscoverMag?a=R126BExi4EI:oLGw6E7EG1s:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DiscoverMag?i=R126BExi4EI:oLGw6E7EG1s:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\"></img></a></div><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/DiscoverMag/~4/R126BExi4EI\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\"/>") (feedburner:origLink nil "http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/CosmicVarianceBlog/~3/rt9KfavAnyk/")) (item nil (title nil "Friday Fluff – October 29th, 2010 | Gene Expression") (link nil "http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/DiscoverMag/~3/KoWKk