s8:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DiscoverMag?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\"></img></a><a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DiscoverMag?a=Sny0g2vjLCE:UBEyJvtQas8:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DiscoverMag?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" border=\"0\"></img></a><a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DiscoverMag?a=Sny0g2vjLCE:UBEyJvtQas8:F7zBnMyn0Lo\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DiscoverMag?i=Sny0g2vjLCE:UBEyJvtQas8:F7zBnMyn0Lo\" border=\"0\"></img></a><a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DiscoverMag?a=Sny0g2vjLCE:UBEyJvtQas8:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DiscoverMag?i=Sny0g2vjLCE:UBEyJvtQas8:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\"></img></a></div><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/DiscoverMag/~4/Sny0g2vjLCE\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\"/>" "http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/DiscoverMag/~3/Sny0g2vjLCE/" (19659 12540) old 5 nil nil ((title nil "Plastic Chemical BPA Linked to Lower Sperm Count & Quality | 80beats") (link nil "http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/DiscoverMag/~3/Sny0g2vjLCE/") (description nil "A new study of 218 Chinese men found that even low levels of the controversial plastics chemical bisphenol A (BPA) can lower sperm quality and count.
